<li><strong>Species & Finish:</strong> Walnut Natural (bases), Maple Polar (uppers)</li>
<li><strong>Hardware:</strong> Satin Brass pulls & faucets</li>
<li><strong>Extras:</strong> Full-height fridge panels, custom dog feeding bay, furniture toe kicks on island</li>
</ul>

<p>Contractor: Norton Custom Construction. Location: Denver, Colorado.</p>

